    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. you mentioned the \"challenges of transitioning\" but it feels like you're being pretty vague about the actual impact on people. for like, the coal towns in western pa, isn't this basically just cutting off their main way of making money? how are they supposed to survive if the subsidies are gone?",
