    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the retraining stuff but it feels like you're saying the transition is \"undeniable\" and \"critical\" like there's no other way it could go. wouldn't someone argue that keeping the coal industry stable is just as important for the state's economy as the green stuff? seems like you're leaning pretty hard into the idea that the shift is just something that has to happen.",
